{"type": "article", "id": 32518, "title": "这些吹制玻璃，演绎的是一出“布与火之歌”｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-09-22T23:09:10Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 33067, "name": "Tough Slate Design"}, {"id": 25699, "name": "Ex.t"}, {"id": 33068, "name": "LuDela"}, {"id": 17876, "name": "Sebastian Herkner"}, {"id": 33069, "name": "Fabio Vogel"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 131, "image": "img/article/article_show/201609222049348SeKMnWDG50ugIxB.jpg", "contents": "<p>          </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>105 Itr Formen by Fabio Vogel</h3><p>布料与火焰，这两者结合后会产生怎样的创意？德国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.fabiovogel.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Fabio Vogel</a> 利用防火布料对花瓶的形态进行了一次探索，得益于模具的塑形，你可以在这套名为 <a href=\"http://www.fabiovogel.com/105-ltr-formen\" rel=\"nofollow\">105 Itr Formen</a> 的花瓶上清楚地看到织物的压痕和缝线，每一件都是独一无二的。这些“瑕疵”使花瓶看起来就像是被磨损过或者是缝合而成一样，让人感受到火焰的破坏力与创造力。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205209abMW8RVYxQ7HLTZX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205210O5AecdQ1FEBIuZvY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205210EQXGTdw1Oh7JivrN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205210hiJt0vWxjuFHd4nf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205209JygBchATVRWFodlX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666259\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>LuDela Candle by LuDela</h3><p>不知不觉间，生活中的很多家居用品都走向了智能化的道路，美国公司 <a href=\"https://ludela.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">LuDela</a> 带来的这款同名智能蜡烛就为人们提供了一种更安全的点蜡烛的方式。团队研发了一种名为 Wi-Fire 的技术，通过配套的手机应用，用户能够远程操控蜡烛燃烧、熄灭，还能为它设定燃烧时间和点燃的时机。当内置的蜡烛消耗到一定程度时，用户也会收到相应的提醒。除此之外，LuDela 的测距组件还会在蜡烛发生意外晃动或是倾倒时自动将其熄灭，免去了普通蜡烛带来的安全隐忧。</p><p>你可以通过它的<a href=\"https://ludela.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">官方网站</a>进行订购，不含每年寄送替换蜡烛包的版本售价为 99 美元，LuDela还提供每月寄送蜡烛包的订购服务。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609222052426es2dcyNvg4KuSqk.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.513333\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205239ZOo5sA9CPa61eIqL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562339\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205241uGqONSc90TU12niR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205238pKoQxO2RbSnw8Hvh.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.812162\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205238ciloLQgH2E4XbBFD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.513843\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Plateau Collection by Sebastian Herkner</h3><p>德国设计师 <a href=\"http://www.sebastianherkner.com\" rel=\"nofollow\">Sebastian Herkner</a> 最近为意大利卫浴品牌 <a href=\"http://shop.ex-t.com/en/\" rel=\"nofollow\">ex.t</a> 设计了一套在边缘处附有延伸平台的卫浴家具组合 <a href=\"http://www.ex-t.com/herkner-new/collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Plateau</a>，包括浴缸、洗手台、水槽。延伸出的平台就像是把家具边缘的阴影给实体化了一样，刚好可以用来盛放洗浴用品。Herkner 为 Plateau 系列设计的三款<a href=\"http://www.ex-t.com/page/plateau-mirror-s/\" rel=\"nofollow\">镜子</a>也有着类似的“阴影”，它其实是一面釉面玻璃，有四种颜色可选。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609222053448yocsvV6OKkPH3hS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.738281\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205344zPFaN6dlOQjpRITx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205344ZXjHOzxDldgBs4fy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205345V293KAJFr7NGP15m.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205345Foh952OVmYWcRHNB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205345N3nElrxWyL2S9Id7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.411667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><h3>Guard by Victoria Azaidnho Bocconi</h3><p>身着红色制服，头戴一顶黑色的熊皮帽——意大利设计师 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/vic_ab\" rel=\"nofollow\">Victoria Azaidnho Bocconi</a> 根据英国标志性的皇家卫兵，设计了这款名为 Guard 的台灯。简洁的三段式设计忠实再现了卫兵憨态可掬的模样，蓝白色的外包装也特意设计成了一座岗哨，看上去相当可爱。Bocconi 还特意给台灯加上了把手，能当作一盏小提灯使用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205308GCijcVgrAsDBd5ba.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.800000\" data-format=\"gif\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205047DKofPnpthdUjmLzG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667143\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205046GVeaNlTP2dj1r0z6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205047n0gx1bhviuURepWF.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922205045nEvZmuJFbYGg9sRT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665833\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><p>          </p><h3>ZEIº by Timeular</h3><p>Timeular 是一个由四位重视时间和效率的设计师组成的团队，为了帮助人们战胜拖延，他们打造了这款名为 ZEIº 的时间管理装置。八面体的 ZEIº 仅重 70 克，是一个充满了未来感的高科技“骰子”。用户可以用附赠的笔在它的表面写/画上待办事宜，将计划开工的那面朝上，配套的应用就会开始计时。</p><p>相比其他时间管理方式，它的优势就在于当你完成一件事后，可以直接通过翻转这个小巧的装置开启下一项计时，所有的数据都会被记录在应用中，方便用户回顾从而改善效率。有意思的是，如果你在工作时想玩玩手机，它甚至还会将你这段“摸鱼”的时间也记录在案。你可以通过<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/timeular/zeio-the-most-simple-time-tracking-solution\" rel=\"nofollow\">链接</a>参与众筹，早鸟价为 69 欧元。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922224153CMTR3E78tFeYZvl2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.551471\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922224200iUKv15DIHzlxZ2BF.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"gif\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922224159lrW5ETwGFS80uILm.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.561765\" data-format=\"gif\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922224201qijanQdMIw8G4c2u.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563333\" data-format=\"gif\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922224154BHqpYeRysriSfQCu.png\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.355882\" data-format=\"png\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922224204Wft7DZhxsRkgSn8o.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.563235\" data-format=\"gif\">\n</figure></div><h3>Diablo by Tough Slate Design</h3><p>看到这款由乌克兰 <a href=\"http://toughslatedesign.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Tough Slate Design</a> 工作室设计的功能饮料包装时，你能立刻从鲜亮的红黑配色以及 Diablo 最后那个长出黑角的字母 O 将它和恶魔联系在一起。和其他用鲜艳的配色表现活力的功能饮料包装不同，设计师们希望通过大胆而且直观的细节来表现出 Diablo 含酒精的特点：品牌名选用了被填满的粗体字体，配合猩红色相当醒目；条形码的一端更是做成了扭曲处理，模仿了火焰的效果。六盒装的纸盒包装上的图案看上去就像是无法混合的油与水，又像是从某个黑暗世界迸发出的岩浆。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609222049529rnbuviz6IF4NCDA.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609222049520u4WxBd7CnAiHgfV.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.583000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201609222049519IntFX0OU8McdV4r.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.582667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922204952jZkaCAdsoNKBOFGc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.584000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922204952ktE1U3xKoCX4r0hA.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.565000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160922204952Q2rkFDUCJPfl8N9z.jpeg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.751000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\n</figure></div>"}